CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 19, reads: "2. Representative Howard Harding, Helen Minor, Toni Hinton and representative Charles Muehlman of the A & P Company served hot A & P Coffee to the thousands of coffee drinkers who visited their booth "
TitMainTitle: Howard Harding, Helen Minor, Toni Hinton, and Charles Muehlman, standing in  A. & P Coffee booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956  Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
